news.title: China: Logan Group's liquidation lawsuit adjourned on potential new petitioner
news.para: The latest development came after the Shenzhen developer said on Friday it had signed an agreement with a key bondholder group on the terms of restructuring its $6.6 billion in offshore debt.

news.title: Delhi: LG gives nod to notify 147 acres of land in Rani Khera for industrial development
news.para: The land was transferred to the Delhi State Industrial and Infrastructure Development Corporation (DSIIDC) from the Delhi Development Authority (DDA) in 2007.

news.title: Thane builder sentenced till 'rising of court' in cheque bounce case, fined Rs 41.44 lakh
news.para: Judicial Magistrate First Class, Thane, Harish Pardeshi, convicted Anil Thakurdas Kursija under section 138 of the Negotiable Instruments Act, 1881. He will have to face imprisonment for two more months if he fails to pay the fine in a month.

news.title: Plots unused for a decade, Noida authority cancels 30 allotments
news.para: According to Noida officials, completion and functional certificates were not obtained by 107 IT/ITES firms that were allotted plots after December 2022. In a recent survey, 78 of them were found to be in different stages of construction, while no construction was carried out on 29 plots.

news.title: Can't relax aviation safety norms for Mhada building: Bombay HC
news.para: ​"No relaxation of civil aviation safety norms can be granted only because the project proponent is a public authority. Aviation safety has nothing at all to do with the identity of the developer," said the HC in its January 10 order.

news.title: Mumbai: Survey of Dharavi notified area to kick off in two weeks
news.para: The last survey was carried out by NGO Mashaal in 2009 which mapped 59,000 tenements, most of them owned by fewer than 100 families.

news.title: RBI proposes to tighten norms for accepting public deposits by HFCs
news.para: ​Currently, housing finance companies (HFCs) are allowed to accept or renew public deposits repayable after a period of 12 months or more but not later than 120 months from the date of acceptance or renewal of such deposits, the RBI said in a draft circular, inviting comments by February 29.

news.title: Dharavi residents to get 350 sq ft flats after redevelopment: Adani group
news.para: The Adani group, which is redeveloping Dharavi slums in collaboration with the Maharashtra government, claimed the flat size was "17 per cent more" than what is offered as part of slum redevelopment projects.

news.title: Delhi court reserves order on Supertech chairman's interim bail plea
news.para: Arora has sought interim bail for three months, claiming he was suffering from various ailments. Arora has told the court he has lost around 10 kg since his arrest and required "urgent medical assistance".

news.title: Amitabh Bachchan buys 10,000 sq ft plot worth Rs 14.5 crore in Ayodhya
news.para: According to the sources, the plot measuring around 10,000 square feet, located in 'The Sarayu' project, was sold at Rs 14.5 crore.

news.title: No need for concern over Land Titling act: Andhra Pradesh minister
news.para: Addressing a gathering at patta distribution programme held here on Friday, the revenue minister said that the government had allotted house sites to 30 lakh people and provided help in construction in those lands.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh plans 1,000-acre township in Ayodhya
news.para: The 'New Ayodhya', for which the state government has already secured land, will be India's first vastu-based township, he said.

news.title: Dispute resolution cell to be operational at Odisha RERA
news.para: The platform, called conciliation and dispute resolute (CDR) cell, will allow interested homebuyers and promoters to initiate a conciliation process and arrive at a mutual decision without going to court.

news.title: Delhi-NCR air pollution: Centre bans non-essential construction work
news.para: Anticipating a prolonged period of severe air quality, the committee decided to implement GRAP Stage-III curbs ('severe' air quality index (AQI) range) immediately to prevent further deterioration.

news.title: Goa: GIDC to e-auction 16 plots at Verna under new norms
news.para: The GIDC plans to lease out 16 plots, which measure a total of 2.3 lakh sqm, through the auction for establishment of industrial enterprises in Verna Industrial Estate.

news.title: Fire safety no less vital if building not highrise: Bombay HC
news.para: ​​A division bench of Justices Gautam Patel and Kamal Khata said, “Such a submission, if made, would be thoroughly irresponsible in a city like Mumbai.”

news.title: Site shows dip in registration of construction workers in Delhi
news.para: While workers’ unions claim the drop is due to loopholes in the online registration system, board officials say very few construction workers are turning up for registration.
